WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:02.966
Hmm, hmm.

2
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:10.400
Hmm.

3
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.966
Ah, ah.

4
00:00:15.066 --> 00:00:17.700
Your Majesty, how is the Empress Dowager?

5
00:00:17.733 --> 00:00:19.766
Father and Mother are no longer in serious condition.

6
00:00:19.766 --> 00:00:20.866
That’s good.

7
00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:24.466
It seems that reciting scriptures and praying still has some effect.

8
00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:27.266
Since you’re so worried about Mother,

9
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:28.233
why not

10
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:31.066
Why not what?

11
00:00:31.533 --> 00:00:34.433
Why not have a prince to cheer up Mother?

12
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:39.033
It’s getting late, my lady.

13
00:00:43.566 --> 00:00:46.000
Let’s go tonight to cheer up Mother, shall we?

14
00:00:58.200 --> 00:00:59.900
Report from the Ci Ning Palace:

15
00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:02.433
The Empress Dowager’s condition has suddenly worsened.

16
00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:04.500
Your Majesty,

17
00:01:04.533 --> 00:01:06.400
I have checked the Empress Dowager’s pulse.

18
00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.833
From the pulse,

19
00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.233
the Empress Dowager’s health doesn’t seem unusual.

20
00:01:10.333 --> 00:01:12.166
As for why she has been unwell,

21
00:01:12.166 --> 00:01:15.100
I believe it may not be related to the Empress Dowager herself.

22
00:01:15.100 --> 00:01:16.100
What is it then?

23
00:01:16.466 --> 00:01:19.766
There’s something I’m not sure if I should say.

24
00:01:20.366 --> 00:01:23.000
Perhaps the Empress Dowager has been cursed.

25
00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:24.566
I’ve reviewed the records,

26
00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.733
and there are indeed historical accounts of such things.

27
00:01:26.733 --> 00:01:29.866
Cursed? Is someone really bold enough to use dark arts?

28
00:01:29.933 --> 00:01:32.233
Get someone to immediately search the palace.

29
00:01:32.366 --> 00:01:33.966
Leave no corner unchecked.

30
00:01:33.966 --> 00:01:34.733
Turn this place inside out.

31
00:01:34.733 --> 00:01:36.700
During this investigation,

32
00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:38.700
no one is allowed to enter any palace.

33
00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:40.266
Anyone who tries to force their way in

34
00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:42.000
will be killed on the spot.
